org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.graph.tuples

Class ImportEdge<K extends Comparable<K>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple
      • org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple5<K,K,K,String,Properties>
        • org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.graph.tuples.ImportEdge<K>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - vertex/edge identifier type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ImportEdge<K extends Comparable<K>>
extends org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple5<K,K,K,String,Properties>
    Represents an external edge which can be imported into the EPGM. f0: edge identifier or null f1: source vertex identifier f2: target vertex identifier f3: edge label f4: edge properties
    See Also:
